See the INSTALL file for building instructions and the TODO file for what
still needs to be implemented.

This project on the Web:
Website: http://vifm.sourceforge.net/
SorceForge: http://sourceforge.net/projects/vifm/
GitHub: https://github.com/ksteen/vifm (preferred)
GitHub: https://github.com/xaizek/vifm (might be removed in the future)

If you are interested in playing with the source code.

src/cfg/config.c - reads scripts and manages configuration
src/cfg/info.c - read and write vifminfo
src/engine/cmds.c - command line parsing core
src/engine/completion.c - provides means to fill and get completion list
src/engine/keys.c - analyzes users input
src/engine/options.c - :set command
src/engine/variables.c - handles :let and :unlet commands
src/menus/apropos_menu.c - handles :apropos menu
src/menus/bookmarks_menu.c - handles :marks menu
src/menus/colorscheme_menu.c - handles :colorscheme menu
src/menus/commands_menu.c - handles :command menu
src/menus/dirhistory_menu.c - handles :history menu
src/menus/dirstask_menu.c - handles :dirs menu
src/menus/filetypes_menu.c - handles :file menu
src/menus/find_menu.c - handles :file menu
src/menus/grep_menu.c - hanldes :grep menu
src/menus/history_menu.c - handles :history command menus except directory history
src/menus/jobs_menu.c - handles :jobs menu
src/menus/locate_menu.c - handles :locale menu
src/menus/map_menu.c - handles :map menu
src/menus/menus.c - handles all kinds of menus
src/menus/registers_menu.c - handles :registers menu
src/menus/undolist_menu.c - handles :undolist menu
src/menus/users_menu.c - handles menus created by %m or %M macros
src/menus/vifm_menu.c - handles :vifm (or :version) menu
src/menus/volumes_menu.c - handles :volumes menu on MS Windows systems
src/modes/dialogs/attr_dialog_nix.c - file permissions dialog for *nix systems
src/modes/dialogs/attr_dialog_win.c - file properties dialog for MS Windows systems
src/modes/dialogs/change_dialog.c - change dialog
src/modes/dialogs/sort_dialog.c - dialog to choose sort type
src/modes/cmdline.c - command line mode
src/modes/file_info.c - Control+G
src/modes/menu.c - handles commands in menus
src/modes/modes.c - general code (e.g. before and after key pressed) for modes
src/modes/normal.c - normal mode commands
src/modes/view.c - view mode commands
src/modes/visual.c - implementation of visual mode commands
src/utils/log.c - primitive logging
src/utils/string_array.c - functions to work with arrays of strings
src/utils/tree.c - cache for ga command results
src/utils/utf8.c - functions to handle utf8 strings
src/utils/utils.c - various utilities
src/background.c - runs commands in background
src/bookmarks.c - stores information about bookmarked directories
src/color_scheme.c - color schemes
src/commands.c - handles command line commands
src/commands_completion.c - handles command line completion
src/desktop.c - code that parses *.desktop files on *nix systems
src/dir_stack.c - for :pushd and :popd commands
src/file_magic.c - determines programs associated with file using its mime-type
src/filelist.c - display/redraw/fill list
src/filename_modifiers.c - expands filename modifiers
src/fileops.c - delete/copy/put selected file(s)
src/filetype.c - stores filetype information from vifmrc
src/fuse.c - provides support of FUSE filesystems
src/globals.c - provides support of globals
src/ipc.c - handles communication across instances of vifm
src/macros - code of macros expanding
src/main_loop.c - the main loop
src/ops.c - most of operations performed on file system
src/opt_handlers.c - initialization of options and option change handlers
src/quickview.c - implementation of quick view
src/registers.c - implementation of registers
src/running.c - code of handing file and commands running
src/search.c - code for / and ? commands of normal mode
src/signals.c - handlers for different signals
src/sort.c - sort function
src/status.c - definition of global status structure
src/tags.c - tags for :h completion
src/trash.c - code that handles list of files in trash
src/ui.c - setup_ncurses_interface() and other ui related functions
src/undo.c - stores and handles the undo list
src/version.c - contains git hash
src/vifm.c - contains main() which does basic initialization
src/vifmrc-converter.c - converter for vifmrc, vifminfo and colorscheme files
src/win_helper.c - needed for temporary rights evaluation on Windows
